<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lore Coffee</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-10">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center p-4">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">Lore Coffee</h1>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-6">
                <a href="/" class="hover:text-gray-500">Home</a>
                <a href="/menu" class="hover:text-gray-500">Menu</a>
                <a href="/cart" class="hover:text-gray-500">Cart</a>
                <a href="/profile" class="hover:text-gray-500">Profile</a>
                <a href="/invoice" class="hover:text-gray-500">Invoice</a>
            </nav>
            <button class="md:hidden" id="menu-button">
                <svg id="menu-icon" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16m-7 6h7"></path></svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <!-- Banner Promo -->
        <section class="bg-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Promo Special!</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mt-2">Dapatkan diskon 20% untuk semua varian kopi hingga akhir bulan ini!</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Artikel -->
        <section class="mt-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Tentang Lore Coffee</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
                Lore Coffee adalah tempat terbaik untuk menikmati kopi dengan cita rasa khas. Kami
                menggunakan biji kopi berkualitas tinggi dan diproses dengan teknik yang telah diwariskan
                secara turun-temurun.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
